channel.title: Isle X - [Old School 317] Pking Server
channel.description:
/****************** TO BETA TEST GO ON FORUMS AND DOWNLOAD THE CLIENT *******************\ [size=11pt]http://Isle-X.co.nr/[/size]
Well, i recently decided to make a new server. Now please note, this is not from scratch,
[IMG]http://i191.photobucket.com/albums/z140/yasel16/Forum-Banner.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i191.photobucket.com/albums/z140/yasel16/Isle-X-for-website.gif[/img]
I FAIL AT PHOTOSHOP
My base is Emulous.
First, i added some skills, such as Mining, Fishing, Cooking, Fletching, Runecrafting (base), and firemaking.
I added specials, I only have, Whip, Dragon Dagger ( P+, ++, (s), etc.), Dragon Mace, Granite Maul, Dragon Halberd, Dragon Scimitar (Does not dis-activates prayer protection prayers yet, Just the emote and the gfx) And dragon Longsword.
Also: I have instant double hit. This works for, DDS & Dragon Halberd special attacks.
Also, There are some i can't add, because I'm using 317 cache with my client. There is a downside to 317 cache though... When runescape was 317, they left out a lot of used P-King items. Such as:
Fire cape Gloves (Also known as "Barrows Gloves") Fury Most items past 6500 i believe.
Also, there is no Tzhaar, so this means no Fight Caves or Fight Pits :'(.
Well, that explains it a bit. Now for some pictures.
Actual Whip Emote (If you haven't noticed the emote for 377+ are messed.) [img]http://i191.photobucket.com/albums/z140/yasel16/WhipAttack.jpg[/img]
Some random pictures [High hits because i was potted and praying, also the NPC has like 1 defense] [IMG]http://i191.photobucket.com/albums/z140/yasel16/443.jpg[/img]
Some other random pictures [IMG]http://i191.photobucket.com/albums/z140/yasel16/intahfazez.jpg[/img]
So yeah... If you ask me, my project is about 25% done. There is no training spots (Not sure if going to add training) No way to make money (except skills) No aching yet And along with that some other things.
Of my knowledge i believe my server can hold up to no more then 400 people. Which is fine by me.
So yeah, that's it.
If you would like to test or just help, Add my MSN,
Tehkuban@hotmail.com
Thank you!
